{"tid":1685752,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"11月5號不如搞番個全民V煞日","createTime":"2019-10-31T17:20:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T03:42:24.000Z","uid":171244,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a14ee6dead9ae8d50d00b356a1ab0a158c7ea0fd","tid":1685752,"uid":171244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T17:20:06.000Z","msg":"有睇V煞嘅朋友，應該知我講咩<br />\n(而家唔係想劇透，但以下有Spoiler自行判斷)<br />\nV煞中嘅V嘅原型就係Guy Fawkes， 而喺V煞劇中嘅11月5日，喺現實中係有咁嘅日子，叫<br />\n<br />\n篝火之夜（Guy Fawkes Day/ Bonfire Night）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">Guy Fawkes 喺乜水?</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nGuy Fawkes（1570 -1606）,一位英國天主徒、前軍人、革命者。因眼見當時嘅英國國王占士一世（James I ）對天主教徒嘅種種打壓而策動火藥襲擊Gunpowder Attack （按:一般媒體稱為火藥陰謀，在此作正名為襲擊），企圖於1605年11月15日，國王將出席嘅議會大幕當日，於國會大樓引爆火藥並炸毀當時嘅英國議會大廈。<br />\n<br />\nGuy 因為事情敗露，而於11月4日被擒，次年亦被判死刑<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">11月5日有咩意義？</span></strong><br />\n正因為Guy 所策動嘅襲擊被篤灰，當時嘅國王James I 先可以苟且偷生到。所以，當英國國會通過法案，定每年11月5日為Thanksgiving Day, 慶祝國王死唔L 去。<br />\n<br />\n呢一日，民眾會聚集放煙火，仲會焚燒Guy Fawkes 假人Figure慶祝<br />\n<br />\n隨時間推演，焚燒嘅對象亦變得唔同，除傳統一直會燒嘅Guy Fawkes 之外，仲新加左唔同嘅人物/政要Figures如: 薩達姆 前外相約翰遜 Trxxp 等等<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重點係，篝火之夜已經成為左一個表達政治訴求多於尊重傳統嘅Event <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">我地可以做啲咩</span></strong><br />\n我唔係叫響嗰晚玩火魔法，但係叫得全民V煞日，大家整個V煞面具係基本啦下話<br />\n<br />\n至於燒Figure,咁就緊係<br />\n<strong>用自己方法，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">安全</span></span>咁做啦</strong><br />\n例如:<br />\n喂，你屋企嗰日記念下先人，響化寶盤度燒個林鄭妹仔、若驊妹仔比太公太婆，服待佢地，都得喇掛<br />\n<br />\n又例如<br />\n想重拾中學旅行樂趣，登高去BBQ, 響合法嘅BBQ爐，用下何妖炭精、 孽瘤炭精透爐，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">安全</span></span>，又得姐<br />\n<br />\n點都好，最緊要<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">安全</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">安全</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同埋，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好撚安全</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><br />\n&ldquo;Remember, remember, the 5th of November<br />\nGunpowder, treason and plot;<br />\nI know of no reason, why the gunpowder treason<br />\nShould ever be forgot.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;記住，記住，十一月五號，<br />\n叛國、陰謀、與火藥，<br />\n我唔明白，<br />\n為什麼陰謀會被人忘記。&rdquo;<br />\n------Mother goose鵝媽媽童謠<br />\n<br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QnqgNA3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQnqgNA3.jpg&h=9f777234&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xjJRBup.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxjJRBup.jpg&h=ce895e30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xjtqFV5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxjtqFV5.png&h=82988877&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fNrPn9r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfNrPn9r.jpg&h=75ccfbb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"37e5ee88e359685e80d576d3d7a9a61419cad9fd","tid":1685752,"uid":171244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T17:21:30.000Z","msg":"11月2，維園見"},{"pid":"13f3a348f80a75dd846239b0e6a6e03cc00e6bf0","tid":1685752,"uid":171244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T17:21:43.000Z","msg":"11月2，維園見"},{"pid":"23c33777608a500c069e678b6a1a4610dc244726","tid":1685752,"uid":171244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T17:22:35.000Z","msg":"11月2，維園見"},{"pid":"faaf2b7e511f072b0f2feb8e57ed080b1eb20f46","tid":1685752,"uid":171244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T17:23:08.000Z","msg":"11月2，維園見"},{"pid":"78f2be088b666074627a9d9ac79c50556038a5db","tid":1685752,"uid":171244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T17:23:18.000Z"